---
// The Atelier Contact — Colofón de revista, elegante, minimalista
---

<section id="contacto" class="py-20 md:py-32 border-t border-dmk-muted/10">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      
      <!-- Lado izquierdo: Colofón editorial (7 cols) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-7 space-y-8">
        <div class="font-serif text-sm text-dmk-accent italic tracking-wide">Contacto</div>
        
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl font-light text-dmk-text leading-tight">
          Hablemos de <em class="font-semibold">Dirección</em> Basada en Evidencia
        </h2>
        
        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-dmk-muted leading-relaxed max-w-md">
          Todo proyecto inicia con un diagnóstico de datos. No vendemos presentaciones; co-diseñamos soluciones medibles para directores de empresas en Chile y Latinoamérica.
        </p>

        <div class="space-y-4 pt-8">
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
            <span class="font-serif text-sm text-dmk-muted italic w-20">Dirección</span>
            <span class="font-sans text-sm text-dmk-text">Av. Apoquindo 4800, Las Condes, Santiago</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
            <span class="font-serif text-sm text-dmk-muted italic w-20">Teléfono</span>
            <span class="font-sans text-sm text-dmk-text">+56 2 2244 8800</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-4">
            <span class="font-serif text-sm text-dmk-muted italic w-20">Email</span>
            <span class="font-sans text-sm text-dmk-accent">contacto@datametrik.cl</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Lado derecho: Formulario minimalista (5 cols) -->
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <form class="space-y-6">
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <label class="font-sans text-xs text-dmk-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Nombre</label>
            <input type="text" class="w-full border-b border-dmk-muted/20 bg-transparent py-2 font-sans text-sm text-dmk-text focus:outline-none focus:border-dmk-accent transition-colors"/>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <label class="font-sans text-xs text-dmk-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Email</label>
            <input type="email" class="w-full border-b border-dmk-muted/20 bg-transparent py-2 font-sans text-sm text-dmk-text focus:outline-none focus:border-dmk-accent transition-colors"/>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <label class="font-sans text-xs text-dmk-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Empresa</label>
            <input type="text" class="w-full border-b border-dmk-muted/20 bg-transparent py-2 font-sans text-sm text-dmk-text focus:outline-none focus:border-dmk-accent transition-colors"/>
          </div>
          <div class="space-y-1">
            <label class="font-sans text-xs text-dmk-muted uppercase tracking-wider">Mensaje</label>
            <textarea rows="3" class="w-full border-b border-dmk-muted/20 bg-transparent py-2 font-sans text-sm text-dmk-text focus:outline-none focus:border-dmk-accent transition-colors resize-none"></textarea>
          </div>
          
          <button type="submit" class="mt-4 font-serif text-sm text-dmk-accent italic hover:underline underline-offset-4">
            Enviar mensaje →
          </button>
        </form>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Footer de revista -->
    <div class="mt-24 pt-8 border-t border-dmk-muted/10 flex justify-between items-center">
      <div class="font-serif text-xs text-dmk-muted italic">Dr. Nicolás Márquez · PhD Management · UAI</div>
      <div class="font-sans text-xs text-dmk-muted">© 2026</div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>
